{"type":null,"faqId":17943,"title":"如何开启 GPS 定位？","answer":"<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21pt; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">从状态栏处向下滑动，打开快捷设置面板，点击\n</span><b style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Frutiger Next Com', sans-serif;\">GPS</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">，可快速打开或关闭 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21pt; font-family: 'Frutiger Next Com', sans-serif;\">GPS</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">卫星定位。</span>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21pt; font-family: Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在<b>设置</b>中的<b>全部设置</b>页签下，点击<b>位置信息</b>，点击位置信息开关，开启位置信息服务。然后点击<b>模式</b>，根据需要选择不同的模式。</span>\n<p>\n<br>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":0,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"685","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1420353550000,"seriesProductName":"SC-CL00","visitedTimes":96,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"p